it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface Header

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface Header
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Header'. Header dell'applicazione. comune a tutti i ContentPanel

    The following features are supported:

    • Cod Canale
    • Cod Applicativo
    • Nome Canale
    • Link Canale
    • Nome Applicativo
    • Title
    • Meta Attributes
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getHeader()
